OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FMillions more people will be banned
OL,7,Ffrom using hosepipes as officials warn
OL,8,Fthat drought conditions are
OL,9,Fincreasingly likely while the nation
OL,10,Fswelters in another lengthy heatwave.
OL,12,FAffinity Water became the latest
OL,13,Futility to announce restrictions as
OL,14,Fthe ongoing hot, dry weather and
OL,15,Fhigher-than-usual demand hits supplies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
