OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FThe firm said on Friday afternoon that
OL,7,Fit would introduce a hosepipe ban on
OL,8,FJuly 17, affecting more than three
OL,9,Fmillion customers across Bedfordshire,
OL,10,FBerkshire, Buckinghamshire, Essex,
OL,11,FHertfordshire, Surrey and parts of
OL,12,FLondon.
OL,14,FOn Friday morning, Anglian Water
OL,15,Fannounced a hosepipe ban for its more
OL,16,Fthan five million customers in the
OL,17,FEast of England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
