OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FCustomers will not be allowed to use
OL,7,Fhosepipes for watering gardens,
OL,8,Fwashing cars or filling swimming and
OL,9,Fpaddling pools from 1am on Saturday,
OL,10,Fbut the utility has asked that people
OL,11,F"live within the spirit of these
OL,12,Frestrictions immediately".
OL,14,FOn Thursday, Cambridge Water announced
OL,15,Fa temporary hosepipe ban for its
OL,16,F350,000 customers, marking the first
OL,17,Ftime in three decades that it has
OL,18,Fintroduced the restriction.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
