OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FThe bans join the 850,000 people under
OL,7,Frestrictions in Kent after South East
OL,8,FWater said it was facing significant
OL,9,Fwater shortages.
OL,11,FThe company said the sheer scale of
OL,12,Fthe long heatwave has meant water is
OL,13,Fbeing drawn from their storage tanks
OL,14,Ffaster than it can physically be
OL,15,Ftreated and refilled.
OL,17,FIt comes as temperatures hit 34C on
OL,18,FThursday and are expected to do so
OL,19,Fagain on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
