OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FIn the UK, 2026 has had more days with
OL,7,Ftemperatures above 34C than any other
OL,8,Fyear in history.
OL,10,FSE Water said that despite producing
OL,11,Fan additional 100 million litres a
OL,12,Fday, demand for drinking water needs
OL,13,Fto be reduced to ensure that supply
OL,14,Finterruptions are not experienced
OL,15,Facross its network throughout the
OL,16,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
