OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FThames Water, Britain's biggest water
OL,7,Fservices provider, told ITV News at
OL,8,Fthe start of July it hasn't introduced
OL,9,Fa hosepipe ban despite recently
OL,10,Fboosting supply by one billion litres
OL,11,Fto its 16 million customers in London
OL,12,Fand the Thames Valley.
OL,14,FThe company encourages people to make
OL,15,Fsmall changes, such as fixing leaks,
OL,16,Fturning off taps when brushing teeth,
OL,17,Fusing watering cans instead of
OL,18,Fhosepipes and sprinklers, and tending
OL,19,Fto gardens early in the morning or
OL,20,Flate in the evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
