OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FWhat is a hosepipe ban?
OL,8,FAccording to regulator Ofwat, a
OL,9,Fhosepipe ban (or a Temporary Use Ban
OL,10,Fto use its official name) is a
OL,11,Frestriction imposed by water companies
OL,12,Fto try and save supplies during
OL,13,Fperiods of high demand or low supply,
OL,14,Fgenerally when it has been very dry
OL,15,Fand hot for long periods.
OL,17,FHow is a hosepipe ban enforced?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
