OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1783718417
OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FIn the UK, water firms have the
OL,7,Fauthority to impose fines of up to
OL,8,F#1,000 on anyone who violates the ban
OL,9,Funder the Water Industry Act.
OL,11,FWho has to comply?
OL,13,FYou are only at risk of prosecution if
OL,14,Fthe ban is in place where you live.
OL,16,FWho is exempt from a hosepipe ban?
OL,18,FPeople who are registered disabled,
OL,19,Fblue badge holders or those on a water
OL,20,Fcompany's priority services register
OL,21,Fare among the few exemptions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
