OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FBusinesses where a hosepipe is
OL,7,Fessential, and ponds for the welfare
OL,8,Fof fish or aquatic animals are not
OL,9,Fincluded.
OL,11,FNeither are pools required for medical
OL,12,Ftreatment nor are ornamental fountains
OL,13,Fused for religious purposes.
OL,15,FHow can I water my garden?
OL,17,FWater companies advise watering plants
OL,18,Fwith a can or bucket.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
