OL,3,CHosepipe bans: What you need to know
OL,4,Cas hot weather leads to restrictions
OL,6,FEven during a ban, the use of a
OL,7,Fhosepipe for some gardening
OL,8,Factivities, such as food crops in
OL,9,Fallotments or home gardens, if they
OL,10,Fcannot reasonably be watered with a
OL,11,Fwatering can, is still allowed.
OL,13,FAndrew Tucker, of Thames Water, said:
OL,14,F"We can't do this alone.
OL,16,F"It's important that customers and
OL,17,Fbusinesses work with us to save water
OL,18,Fwhere they can and play their part in
OL,19,Fprotecting our vital resources."
